n.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984467_1022236459704458_1724261035116980719_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=EqqAiB5Ln_IQ7kNvgG9wFzK&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBzrgdDEItZCDzPqsZad0q46SXErpiSIvPiFZHYltxmKQ&oe=676AA65B"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "(Replacement Meta Cover img) Vote 2560x1440.png", "id": "1092892118837385", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003255_1092892122170718_5861729437307828234_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=9XD4Q7SZFWwQ7kNvgGnZLH7&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCot8PKURAJ3-We5d04dBBU_P71zNN-GqvzuuPYdJXXZg&oe=676A9B94"}, "display_name": "Vote", "keywords": ["Vote", "Poll", "Election", "Machine", "America"], "long_description": "# SUPPORT YOUR CANDIDATE\n\n**Current Poll: US Presidential Election!**\n\nCast your vote in the virtual world, no matter where you live! Dive into 'Vote' and experience the thrill of democracy like never before\u2014right from your Meta Quest. Engage, and shape your nation's future in this immersive VR voting simulator. Submit your ballot and obtain a prize for participating!\n{1786136528457732}\n\n**Your vote matters. Make it count!**  \n\nThis is a virtual voting simulator and is not an official voting platform. Votes cast in 'Vote' do not have any legal standing or effect on real-world elections. 'Vote' is a product of Megaverse LLC, a Fun Train company. All rights reserved. \u00a9 2024 Megaverse LLC. Unauthorized use, duplication, or distribution of this material without express and written permission from Megaverse LLC is strictly prohibited.\n{379762491737366}\n{1609938676597010}", "short_description": "Current Poll: US Presidential Election! \nResidents around the world are invited to cast their vote!\n\nVote is a free polling simulator which lets participants cast their virtual ballot in various political elections around the world.  Vote as many times as you like to help pro